creator: AI.io
descriptionHtml:
You have got unclear sound while on call? If yes, then you need to clean phone speaker and improve sound quality.

Sometimes garbase and water get stuck in the phone's speaker and sound getting muffled is common problem world wide.
With this app you can remove water, dust from speaker and clean your speaker sound by playing different type of sound waves.

This speaker cleaner app produce sound and vibration with different frequencies mode that can help to remove dust and water from phone's speaker and fixed speaker sound issue.

Repair my speaker sound app will solve your phone speaker sound problem without any hassle.

There are three ways to clean speaker and repair bad sound.

AUTO CLEAN:- It is a automated process. Just click on start process and it will fix sound problem in 50 second.

MANUAL CLEAN:- In this mode you can pick exact frequency of second for particular speaker.

VIBRATION MODE:- When you use this mode device will be vibrate and try to clean water, dust from speaker.
descriptionShort: Your phone's speaker sound getting muffled? use fix my speaker & improve sound.
